					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12180769#post-4387951</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12180769/scp-4587#post-4387951</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2019 18:27:10 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>classybass</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3667970</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Overall, this gets a +1 from me. That said, I did spot 2 odd things in it:</p> <blockquote> <p>Experiment Log (truncated)</p> </blockquote> <p>While &quot;truncated&quot; does work, I find it a bit weird in this context. I'd think &quot;abridged&quot; would work better.</p> <p>Also, in the experiment log, some of the sub-designations are incorrect:</p> <ul> <li>SCP-4587-117 should be SCP-4587<em>-A</em>-117</li> <li>SCP-4587-210 should be SCP-4587<em>-A</em>-210</li> <li>SCP-4587-528 should be SCP-4587<em>-A</em>-528</li> </ul> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
