					<![CDATA[
						 <p>it's another one of my favorite type of SCPs: recordings that change every time you play them! this is a hilarious take on the 1733 concept, and even better, it's the return of TotleighSoft! i don't think i've seen them involved in an SCP in a while. really good execution on the concept. also, ALAN RICKMAN! absolutely a +1.</p> <p>side note: shouldn't this have a &quot;recording&quot; tag?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
